                    <p class="text-left">信息编辑完成点击“确认参保”进入社保订单页。点击“提交订单”进行支付。</p>
                    <img src="~/Content/img/buy-5.png" alt="进入添加参保人" />
                </div>
            </div>
            <!--如何查询办理结果-->
            <div class="intro-buy text-center am-padding-horizontal">
                <img src="~/Content/img/buy-6.png" alt="如何查询办理结果" class="am-margin-top-lg" />
                <div>
                    <p class="text-left">在首页“我的帐户-我的订单”会显示社保或公积金订单状态，详情</p>
                    <img src="~/Content/img/buy-7.png" alt="缴社保" />
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
